Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.51,0:00:55.09,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)}満開の愛を載せて　笑顔  届きますように
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.10,0:01:05.70,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}新しい世界の始まり　My Dear　Dear
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.81,0:01:11.71,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,イージーだった私に　論外全部サヨナラ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.73,0:01:15.37,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)}後悔なんで　もうしないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.69,0:01:23.45,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,どんな困難なことも　ハッピーに変換したら
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.46,0:01:29.28,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)}Shine  朝日も手招きしているよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.29,0:01:32.23,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,不安にこっそり震えてても強がって
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.29,0:01:35.26,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,胸　ギュッと振り絞ったら加速して
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.30,0:01:41.25,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,勇気感じる　だって君がすぐ傍に
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.29,0:01:47.26,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)}一緒にどこまでも　進もう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.27,0:01:54.43,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)}乗っちゃった追い風に　精一杯　届けたいからね
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.44,0:01:59.22,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)}君へと繋ぐココロ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.26,0:02:07.09,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)}最新のコラムに　めいいっばい　気持ち込めたから
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.10,0:02:15.91,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,100)}ときめいて　どこでも行けるよ　My Dear　My Dear
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.51,0:00:55.09,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)}载上盛放的爱  希望笑容能够送达
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.10,0:01:05.70,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}新世界的开始  My Dear  Dear
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.81,0:01:11.71,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,曾经安逸的我  告别所有的不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.73,0:01:15.37,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)}已经不会再后悔了哟
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.69,0:01:23.45,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,不管是怎样的困难  也要设法变成快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.46,0:01:29.28,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)}Shine  朝阳也在招手喔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.29,0:01:32.23,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,不安时偷偷地颤抖也要逞强
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.29,0:01:35.26,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,揪紧了心一口气全力加速
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.30,0:01:41.25,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,感受到了勇气  因为你就在我身旁
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.29,0:01:47.26,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)}一起走遍天涯海角吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.27,0:01:54.43,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)}乘上了爱之风  竭尽全力去传递
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.44,0:01:59.22,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)}和你相连的心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.26,0:02:07.09,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)}在最新的新闻栏里  将所有的心情都倾注进去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.10,0:02:15.91,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,100)}心跳不已  无论何处都能前往  My Dear  My Dear
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.82,0:00:30.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,欢…欢迎大家回来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.17,0:00:35.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.46,0:00:46.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,奶奶  秋老虎说的就是这个时候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.53,0:02:22.90,biaoti,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(543,405)\fad(500,0)}第一次的、思念
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.07,0:02:35.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是什么～呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.15,0:02:55.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.04,0:02:59.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对…对不起  小遥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.32,0:03:02.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.25,0:03:10.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小屁屁～小胸部～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.49,0:03:14.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请…请放开我！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.85,0:03:16.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要～嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.82,0:03:20.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,放·开·我·啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.85,0:03:24.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你给我自重点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.69,0:03:26.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯～但是～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.28,0:03:29.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别用筷子指人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.35,0:03:31.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是但是但是但是～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.60,0:03:31.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.79,0:03:34.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得胸部也被摸了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.39,0:03:40.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是～那可是绝无仅有的良机～嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.63,0:03:44.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且  小屁屁～小胸部～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.23,0:03:47.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.96,0:03:53.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是挺好吗  多亏小遥垫在下面你才没受伤
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.44,0:03:56.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对…啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.72,0:04:01.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明明救了我  我却连声谢谢都没说  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.14,0:04:04.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小佳奈～
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.51,0:04:07.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,该道歉的不是佳奈吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.80,0:04:09.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  你也太天真了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.56,0:04:15.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是天真  佳奈是温柔啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.24,0:04:16.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小梦…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.58,0:04:30.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,优希对不起啦  给优希也摸摸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.68,0:04:39.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,话说  佳奈为什么要爬树？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.60,0:04:42.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是  因为太热  就忍不住…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.17,0:04:45.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且文太也在上面
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.24,0:04:46.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么太热就要爬树？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.02,0:04:51.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是奶奶教我的  猫知道哪里凉快
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.14,0:04:54.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,原来是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.28,0:04:58.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这个我也知道  球藻说过的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.42,0:05:01.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请问  球藻是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.05,0:05:04.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因为是北海道出身所以叫球藻
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.81,0:05:08.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是啦  我是问那是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.99,0:05:14.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,球藻姐就是…我想想  怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.74,0:05:16.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是去年还在这里的人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.69,0:05:18.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,反正就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.96,0:05:22.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是风新开业以来的废柴员工
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.72,0:05:29.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,风新开业以来的…废柴？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.26,0:05:33.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那…该不会…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.16,0:05:43.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,报纸被狗咬住  然后扯坏了之类的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.75,0:05:44.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.10,0:05:50.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看错了名字  把报纸送错之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.76,0:05:52.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那都是家常便饭了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.28,0:05:56.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因为迷路  报纸很晚才送到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.41,0:05:59.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,客户来投诉  我都不知道过几次歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.46,0:06:05.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,顺便因为回来得也很晚  急着做早饭的菜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.03,0:06:09.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,把文太的猫罐头当成青花鱼罐头开了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.81,0:06:14.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没有  她根本就没回得来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.93,0:06:17.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以老要人去接她
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.31,0:06:21.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了  我还自己回得来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.78,0:06:25.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  代理可是挺开心的～哟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.49,0:06:27.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,跟小球藻在一起的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.99,0:06:30.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,才没有  有什么好开心的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.71,0:06:34.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是啊  虽然嘴上碎碎念个不停
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.59,0:06:36.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,却经常跟她黏在一起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.47,0:06:37.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.79,0:06:39.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,说笑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.22,0:06:42.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我为什么要跟那种磨人的人在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.44,0:06:47.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是越磨人的孩子越可爱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.54,0:06:51.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,无稽之谈！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.65,0:06:57.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我先去休息了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.52,0:07:06.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我好像惹代理生气了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.85,0:07:10.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没事啦  她只是闹别扭而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.18,0:07:13.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我想起来～啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.12,0:07:15.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.47,0:07:20.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你们还记得不  去年春天下大雪那天
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.02,0:07:23.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,记得记得
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.82,0:07:28.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大雪是指那次十八年一遇的大寒流吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.44,0:07:32.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对对  那一天啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.21,0:07:44.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎  好惨好惨  在街上连人带车地摔倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.72,0:07:46.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,报纸没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.24,0:07:52.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没…没事倒是没事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.52,0:07:56.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,难道又是球藻姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.47,0:07:58.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.76,0:08:01.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有让她带上手机出门吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.57,0:08:03.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,都挂在她脖子上了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.74,0:08:07.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.51,0:08:11.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  姐姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.97,0:08:15.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小遥  怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.47,0:08:16.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不够
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.45,0:08:19.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么不够  晨报还是体育报？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.26,0:08:24.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,女孩子的爱啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.43,0:08:27.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,给我爱  请给我爱～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.88,0:08:34.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,算了算了  冷静啊代理
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.27,0:08:42.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,代理？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.04,0:08:46.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,去接球藻姐吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.28,0:08:47.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.39,0:08:51.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等等  今天我去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.16,0:08:54.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在雪里走很辛苦的  又危险
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.16,0:08:56.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.15,0:09:00.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不行  今天我去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.87,0:09:03.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且说不定球藻姐会打电话来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.05,0:09:06.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这里还是留个人在比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.90,0:09:11.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.92,0:09:16.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.46,0:09:24.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小梦  你现在在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.91,0:09:27.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在天神附近
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.30,0:09:30.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,猜对了  能拜托你个事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.94,0:09:35.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.24,0:09:38.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,优希那边我来说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.69,0:09:42.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  也让小遥来帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.63,0:09:53.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,给我爱  请给我爱～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.30,0:10:00.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好像会很麻烦  算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.42,0:10:31.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊  真是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.59,0:10:40.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是球藻姐的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.16,0:10:58.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,该不会…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.76,0:11:01.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,佳奈！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.64,0:11:02.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,日记
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.98,0:11:06.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,佳奈～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.91,0:11:07.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,日记！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.63,0:11:15.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,球藻掉到河里了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.83,0:11:18.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧  一般都会这么想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.70,0:11:20.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也急了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.53,0:11:25.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明明说了交给我  结果还是打了电话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.32,0:11:28.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.85,0:11:39.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  雏田？找到姐姐了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.48,0:11:42.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,代理  不妙啊  球藻姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.47,0:11:51.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办  是不是应该叫警察来？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.37,0:11:58.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,代理？喂  你在听吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.52,0:12:00.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,代理  代理！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.23,0:12:07.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎  这下糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.23,0:12:11.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.91,0:12:12.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小遥？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.96,0:12:14.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么  是雏田啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.08,0:12:18.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小球藻吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.86,0:12:20.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.34,0:12:24.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没事  看样子她刚走
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.94,0:12:27.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,跑一跑应该能追上的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.49,0:12:29.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那代理就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.44,0:12:32.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.95,0:12:39.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小雏  不在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.48,0:12:42.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,球藻姐吧  其实我现在正…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.76,0:12:45.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是啦  是小猫不在
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.24,0:12:50.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,球藻的小猫朋友少了一只
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.73,0:12:52.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,去哪了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.28,0:12:57.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小梦  总之你先回店里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.08,0:12:58.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.48,0:13:04.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这次又是代理…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.48,0:13:08.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了  我马上跟优希汇合后就回去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.17,0:13:16.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我忘了告诉她找到球藻的围巾了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.12,0:13:31.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,代理跑得还真快～啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.79,0:14:12.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咲妃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.38,0:14:27.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是担心死啦  刚才听小遥说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.24,0:14:29.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我说  很难受
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.02,0:14:33.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.38,0:14:38.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋  我很担心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.86,0:15:01.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,代理居然像那样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.79,0:15:04.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是说～嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.65,0:15:09.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,平时那么不坦率的代理居然说「我很担心啊」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.97,0:15:14.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,坦率的代理太美～了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.25,0:15:21.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小遥  扣薪水
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.94,0:15:26.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么  代理有在听啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.44,0:15:29.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么嘛  又不是什么好害羞的事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.83,0:15:31.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雏田也扣薪水
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.81,0:15:33.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为啥！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.31,0:15:39.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,其他人也一样  都扣薪水扣薪水扣薪水！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.15,0:15:53.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,居然扣薪水
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.14,0:15:55.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,很过分吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.97,0:16:02.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是说啊  真是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.82,0:16:12.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,来  庆祝佳奈也被扣薪水  用大米可乐干杯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.92,0:16:20.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  球藻真是好厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.02,0:16:21.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.13,0:16:26.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因为她会用能让代理变坦率的魔法嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.59,0:16:31.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,魔法啊  真不错
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.57,0:16:35.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想学～啊  那个魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.01,0:16:42.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,然后  就能随时随地跟坦率的代理…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.73,0:16:46.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  小遥遥  快回来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.46,0:16:49.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  如果不是魔法的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.43,0:16:53.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,代理为什么能在球藻面前那么坦率呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.35,0:16:58.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一定是发生了什么我们不知道的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.07,0:17:01.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,发生了什么事…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.61,0:17:02.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对对
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.90,0:17:05.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,佳奈觉得是发生了什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.85,0:17:08.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这个嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.42,0:17:12.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是把围巾给了猫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.64,0:17:17.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,球藻一定非常温柔的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.42,0:17:18.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.23,0:17:24.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  大家也都这么温柔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.31,0:17:28.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我还是不太明白
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.53,0:17:37.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  那还真是稀奇～啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.53,0:17:41.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,的确  代理很少那么坦率的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.65,0:17:43.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是～啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.26,0:17:48.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是指由小球藻去接代理这件事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.19,0:17:53.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对啊  球藻姐总是迷路
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.77,0:17:55.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那是她第一次接别人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.52,0:17:56.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不对哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.31,0:18:01.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,球藻那之后很快就毕业了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.16,0:18:04.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是第一次也是最后一次接人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.67,0:18:07.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,毕业
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.34,0:18:12.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  真是太好了～啊  小球藻
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.48,0:18:17.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在最后的最后  终于没让人去接她了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.94,0:18:23.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过啊  那时候准确来说应该是代理去接她的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.04,0:18:26.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是～啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.62,0:18:28.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.37,0:18:37.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,毕业吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.54,0:19:13.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还没睡吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.35,0:19:17.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不  只是有点口渴了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.75,0:19:19.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么  佳奈也口渴了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.17,0:19:24.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊  老盯着我看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.10,0:19:25.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.71,0:19:34.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.75,0:19:35.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.85,0:19:38.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,代理不觉得寂寞吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.93,0:19:39.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.24,0:19:43.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,球藻从这里毕业了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.36,0:19:47.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是觉得折腾人的家伙走了  轻松了不少
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.29,0:19:51.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  代理不是对球藻…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.91,0:19:54.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不  那个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.48,0:20:00.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是我跟大家分开了的话  一定会很寂寞的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.19,0:20:08.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,佳奈你有一天也是会离开这里的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.33,0:20:13.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗  我也会…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.56,0:20:15.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行了  快去睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.67,0:20:17.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还有两个小时就该起床了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.97,0:20:19.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真的！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.45,0:20:22.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.70,0:20:23.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.36,0:20:40.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是天神的小猫
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.67,0:20:44.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  因为在原来的地方没看到它
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.87,0:20:45.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我就到处找了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.33,0:20:48.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  我们才到处找了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.63,0:20:52.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗  也对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.49,0:21:00.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你明天就走了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.10,0:21:02.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.62,0:21:06.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,房间收拾好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.47,0:21:08.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.58,0:21:12.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个  咲妃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.67,0:21:13.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.71,0:21:17.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你是自己找到这里来的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.80,0:21:19.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.63,0:23:32.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,下一话  「第一次的、减肥？」
